description:
<Pre-order bonus items>
・ProfiCards: A set of 15 cards featuring promotional art of the series main characters
These images can be used on player ProfiCards that are used to record gameplay results. Exchange ProfiCards featuring special designs with friends and multiplayer opponents.

*Only available to customers who pre-order by 20:59 (PT) on February 15, 2023.
*An internet connection is required to obtain the digital bonus items.
*Content and specifications may be altered without prior warning.
name: Warriors of Light (Musician) – set of 15 ProfiCard pictures
